{"tid":316844,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【估中無獎】鄭錦滿今日(7.11)上庭，熱血會有幾多人幾多支旗去法院捧場呢","createTime":"2017-07-11T04:51:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T02:59:26.000Z","uid":122532,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80a91bbb1528ddeb1c3b46b5594e59e3eb2e434a","tid":316844,"uid":122532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T04:51:59.000Z","msg":"鄭錦滿涉偷9本圖書　控方呈上被告自白短片<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/450754\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F450754&d=vG6ne3CU2QwHKE9ve8qjYZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=9d06dac2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F450754&h=3f349b46\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/450754</a><br />\n<br />\n早前因違反「佔旺」清場禁制令，而被判監三個月的熱血公民副主席鄭錦滿，涉去年3月在九龍公共圖書館偷竊9本圖書，後被控一項盜竊罪，案件今日在九龍城裁判法院⁠⁠⁠⁠審訊。控方將會呈上一段39分鐘的圖書館閉路電視片段，以及一段鄭上傳Facebook的自白短片。據悉，鄭在影片內呼籲市民以自己的方式將簡體字書下架。<br />\n<br />\n事發去年3月29日，鄭在九龍公共圖書館4樓兒童圖書館將9 本兒童圖書放在垃圾筒中，將過程拍攝並上傳在「四眼哥哥」（鄭錦滿）的Facebook專頁上。<br />\n<br />\n法庭記者：李芷恩<br />\n<br />\n** 上年四月警署門外片段<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ttYED8ZmeHU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DttYED8ZmeHU&d=vG6ne3CU2QwHKE9ve8qjYZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=1802adf0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ttYED8ZmeHU</a><br />\n<br />\n** 四能眼毀書片段<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WfEl3c_9G6c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWfEl3c_9G6c&d=vG6ne3CU2QwHKE9ve8qjYZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=133affa1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WfEl3c_9G6c</a>"},{"pid":"a587c54ae5e6c4eabfcbe3b1d055016829f691a2","tid":316844,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T05:08:42.000Z","msg":"自己做埋d on9野，有邊個會支持？"},{"pid":"64b6d62b16773a3cd881045c7b